      "text": "\n\n\n\n- Run Unit tests\n- Builds Docker image\n- Connects to ECR via OIDC\n- Pushes image to ECR\n- Update image tag in Kubernetes deployment manifest",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wXj_tRv7vsO-bE35EvcGm",
      "originalText": "\n\n\n\n- Run Unit tests\n- Builds Docker image\n- Connects to ECR via OIDC\n- Pushes image to ECR\n- Update image tag in Kubernetes deployment manifest",
      "autoResize": true,
